body:
---

## What happened

Similar to issues #5477, the project does not use Flutter. it's just one of many plugins loaded in IDEA.

## Version information

IntelliJ IDEA `2021.1.1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 56.0.5` • Dart plugin `211.7233`

No Flutter sdk configured.
